MALACAÑANG MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 157

RESERVING FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF LIBERTAD ELEMENTARY SCHOOL A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN THE BARRIO OF LIBERTAD, MUNICIPALITY OF KOLAMBUGAN, PROVINCE OF LANAO DEL NORTE, ISLAND OF MINDANAO

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, CORAZON C. AQUINO, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale or settlement and reserve for school site purposes of the Libertad Elementary School under the administration of the Secretary of Education, Culture and Sports, subject to private rights, if any there be, a certain parcel of land of the public domain situated in the Barrio of Libertad, Municipality of Kolambugan, Province of Lanao del Norte, Island of Mindanao, more particularly described as follows:

Lot No. 7167, PLS-89

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot No. 7167, Pls-89, Kolambugan Public Land Subdivision), situated at the barrio of Libertad, Municipality of Kolambugan, Province of Lanao del Norte, Island of Mindanao, bounded on the S., W., and N., along lines 9-1-2-3-4-5-6 by Lot 6, Ccs-12-000034, identical to lot 7168, pls-89, Kolambugan Public Land Subdivision; on the NE., along lines 6-7-8 by Lot PC-1149, (REI-2680), Findlay Millar Timber Company; and on the E., along line 8-9 by Lot 3, Ccs-12 000034, identical to Lot 7165, Pls-89, Kolambugan Public Land Subdivision. Beginning at a point marked “1” of Lot 7167, Pls-89, Being S. 86°05′ W., 1351.80 M. from B.L.L.M. #1, Kolambugan Public Land Subdivision, Pls-89;

26.15 meters to point 2;

64.35 meters to point 3;

38.36 meters to point 4;

7.85 meters to point 5;

63.11 meters to point 6;

31.05 meters to point 7;

76.67 meters to point 8;

41.56 meters to point 9;

108.46 meters to point of

beginning,

containing an area of TEN THOUSAND (10,000) SQUARE METERS, more or less. Date of survey, November 3, 1980, by Vicente B. Militante, Sr. Geodetic Engineer.

(Note: This is Lot 5, Css-12-000034, identical to Lot No. 7167, Pls-89, Kolambugan Public Land Subdivision as described in the approved plan of Ccs-12-000034 in file with the District and Land Office No. XII-3, Tubod, Lanao del Norte.)

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 21st day of September in the year of Our Lord, Nineteen Hundred and Eighty-Seven.

(Sgd.) CORAZON C. AQUINO

By the President: (Sgd.) CATALINO MACARAIG, JR. Acting Executive Secretary

